verses.text:
There's life in a look at the sacred cross, Jesus has said, "Look unto me;"
I'll look to the cross ev'ry day and hour, Trusting the promise God has given;
O When first to the Saviour I raised my eyes, Sweet was the smile that fell on me.

chorus.text:
In a look... there's life for thee, In a look at Calvary;
In a look there's life for thee, In a look at Calvary;
Blessed thought, salvation free, By a look... at Calvary (at Calvary).
Blessed thought, salvation free, By a look
